FAQ

For developer inquiries, please email developer@rntrx.io

What is RntrX?

RntrX is a safe, secure, and scalable platform that powers RntrCheck and many other top services for the rental industry. It offers a wide range of capabilities and features that are continuously improved and expanded. These features and applications can be used individually or together, all aimed at ensuring your business, properties, and tenants thrive.

What is RntrCheck?

ntrCheck is a comprehensive tenant screening platform designed to help landlords, property managers, and tenants streamline the rental application process.

How do I sign up for RntrCheck?

To sign up, click on the "Sign Up" button on the home page. Choose your user type (Tenant, Property Manager, or Landlord), fill in your full name, create a password, and agree to the terms and conditions and privacy policy.

How do I verify my account?

After signing up, you will receive an OTP verification code via email. Enter this code in the provided field on the verification screen to verify your account.

What should I do if I don't receive the OTP verification code?

If you don't receive the OTP code, click on the "Send Again" button to resend the code. Make sure to check your spam or junk folder in your email.

How can I reset my password?

If you forget your password, click on the "Forgot Password?" link on the login page. Enter your email address, and you will receive a code to reset your password. Follow the instructions to set a new password.

How do I edit my profile information?

To edit your profile, go to the "Profile" section on your dashboard. You can update your personal information, upload a new profile picture, and save the changes.

What should I do if I need to delete my account?

If you need to delete your account, navigate to the "Profile" section and click on "Delete Account." Please note that this action is irreversible.

Other questions

For more details about the process and screening services, please visit the "Support" tab within the application. For any additional questions about RntrCheck, feel free to email us at info@rntrcheck.com.
